00:00:14.780 --> 00:00:18.980 align:middle line:84%
the time or skate through
life without slowing down?

00:00:18.980 --> 00:00:22.370 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps the real path to
unlocking our hidden potential

00:00:22.370 --> 00:00:25.610 align:middle line:84%
requires us to take a step
back every now and then

