unlocking our hidden potential.

00:00:48.860 --> 00:00:52.500 align:middle line:84%
And that is forgiveness
and self-care.

00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:54.390 align:middle line:90%
I like what Anne Lamot said.

00:00:54.390 --> 00:00:56.910 align:middle line:84%
"Everything will work
again if you unplug it

00:00:56.910 --> 00:01:01.480 align:middle line:84%
